<div class="newsletter-wrapper">
  <h3>🎯 訂閱電子報與 YouTube 頻道</h3>
  <p>掌握最新得 JavaScript 技術與免費教學，別錯過每週的技術交流！</p>
  
  <div class="subscription-actions">
    <a href="https://youtube.com/@AndysTV" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-youtube">
      ▶️ 訂閱 YouTube 頻道
    </a>
    <a href="https://buttondown.email/YOUR_ACCOUNT" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-newsletter">
      ✉️ 訂閱免費技術報
    </a>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .newsletter-wrapper {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .newsletter-wrapper h3 {
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .newsletter-wrapper p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .subscription-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-youtube, .btn-newsletter {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-youtube {
    background: #ef4444;
    color: white;
  }

  .btn-youtube:hover {
    background: #dc2626;
  }

  .btn-newsletter {
    background: #3b82f6;
    color: white;
  }

  .btn-newsletter:hover {
    background: #2563eb;
  }
</style>
